    "deployed": false,
    "note": "Design-first artifact only \u2014 describes the MCP tool surface, not a running server. Tool input/output schemas $ref the same object schemas as the OpenAPI; each tool maps to an OpenAPI operationId. Operationalizes the TLC's batch-only open data (monthly parquet trip files + flat Socrata license snapshots) behind one agent contract, and adds a net-new license-application write.",
